thread.title_full: Del City reviewed by Ernest Christman

author: Ernest Christman
title: Ernest Christman
text: When I ordered the parts that I needed I don't know if I gave the wrong numbers or the parts were mis labled. But I EXPLAINED TO THEM WHAT WAS WRONG WITH THE ORDER AND THEY HAD THE PARTS SENT OUT RIGHT AWAY AND I RECEIVED IN A DAY OR TWO. NOW THAT WAS EXCELLENT BUSINESS. YOU CAN NOT ASK FOR BETTER SERVICE THAN THAT....
